There are some issues currently with some other gyros, but navX-sensors are working w/the 2022 firmware.

You didn’t say what language, what board type, and what interface you are using. We recommend I2C (on the MXP port), as a few teams (but not all) are seeing issue with the SPI interface this year.

If you have continued problems, be sure to post the driver station logs as there are several important things usually in the logs when a problem occurs.

Cheers,

  • scott
